-"Não deem ouvidos a elas."

1080
01:25:14,922 --> 01:25:16,922
...mas posso pelo menos saber o porquê?

1081
01:25:17,797 --> 01:25:19,630
Por que preciso morrer?

1082
01:25:22,213 --> 01:25:24,755
Jecheon no Leste, Taebaek no Oeste,
Jeongseon no Norte

1083
01:25:24,838 --> 01:25:26,380
e Danyang no Sul.

1084
01:25:26,588 --> 01:25:28,338
