1239
01:38:35,130 --> 01:38:36,547
Ela me mandou verificar.

1240
01:38:38,255 --> 01:38:39,963
Ela me falou para verificar a marca.

1241
01:38:40,922 --> 01:38:42,088
Qual marca?

1242
01:38:48,713 --> 01:38:50,172
