1243
01:38:59,255 --> 01:39:00,422
Gwangmok.

1244
01:39:00,963 --> 01:39:02,380
É essa a lábia da serpente.

1245
01:39:02,463 --> 01:39:03,838
A lábia dela o enganou.

1246
01:39:06,005 --> 01:39:08,797
